{"tid":272712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(重溫) 90後「蘋果幸運哥」抽中次籌 首期唔使父","createTime":"2017-06-06T04:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T08:29:14.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dea0cf3a3e1a2e5e09cde2ddb44fb8c8423b6d22","tid":272712,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T04:40:49.000Z","msg":"冇護士女友 母親冇改嫁 冇借non mean 炒股<br />\n每日只係腳踏實地打工<br />\n為上車，佢天天食特價canteen 飯<br />\n為上車，佢只坐公司車<br />\n<br />\n終於，在幸運之神眷顧下抽中居屋次籌，有望上車<br />\n佢係邊個?佢係是我哋「蘋果幸運哥」同事間叫佢做「鏗少」，無論市場話抽iphone，定抽匯豐紀念鈔，佢次次參與，今次見全港人人抽居屋，佢一於都唔執輸，抽埋一份，「初頭都是抱住抽下嘅心態」，結果佢抽中80號籌，排第二組別。<br />\n過去幾個月，佢完全沒有為中居屋做準備，事關佢都唔覺得自己會中獎，「由細到大，都未中過獎，<span style=\"color: red;\">估唔到今次抽中</span>」。他透過<span style=\"color: red;\">白表單身人士身份抽中第二組別</span>。佢話，今日開始做功課，現場視察幾個居屋，睇下有咩優劣。<br />\n講到首期約20萬元至30萬元，佢坦言，可以靠自己嘅積蓄支付，唔使靠屋企人。若果有幸抽中，日後居屋月供約1萬元，他相信，死慳死抵，都應該供得掂。不過心情有少少矛盾，因為居屋日後轉售要補地價，心情十五十六，來緊同屋企人商量下，見步行步。<br />\n他希望小編幫手落呢句：「希望老闆加多啲人工！」"},{"pid":"27505337117103af2879cb1cedbc6f323fe347b0","tid":272712,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T04:41:25.000Z","msg":"幸運哥揀左樓未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20150326/large/1427373917_4e1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20150326%2Flarge%2F1427373917_4e1b.jpg&h=c55fae6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b4c8d93598156f70aa368d61a3d58d1e7be5695","tid":272712,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:00:10.000Z","msg":"炒iPhone炒紀念鈔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f8436b12f8ba83968dceb57b3b86a2f34552d6","tid":272712,"uid":52010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:01:27.000Z","msg":"抽中就有樓揀咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e54f45913891b15ee330c821775bc2da9f52a5","tid":272712,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:01:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死慳死抵，都應該供得掂</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁就唔好供啦. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05ea066f04271974ef5248d1954413335174801","tid":272712,"uid":25099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:03:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>炒iPhone炒紀念鈔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca501b872e56e1a96e805a5bdcd7eff1019be42","tid":272712,"uid":26345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:05:38.000Z","msg":"公屋都要供1萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625d9276a34f844688f4f751502f02295dbd7e26","tid":272712,"uid":26345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:06:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公屋都要供1萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSor 居屋，但都要1萬，好貴"},{"pid":"c293eb2fa2f08c1ece3fc3ad23291537133ad42d","tid":272712,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:44:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抽中就有樓揀咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b66b01d22de5b4c6929509cb092bd2acf94552","tid":272712,"uid":105421,"like